{"tid":1887092,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"港航向部分員工發解僱信    今日為最後上班日","createTime":"2020-02-19T10:06:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-19T10:12:50.000Z","uid":79563,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"697c4b67cb2c5f370fe7274470f70962b608bdf8","tid":1887092,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T10:06:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/b7piO2RzIjINK5go7UdR_A--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAwO2lsPXBsYW5l/http://media.zenfs.com/en_us/News/singtao/20200219a150710.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2Fb7piO2RzIjINK5go7UdR_A--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAwO2lsPXBsYW5l%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen_us%2FNews%2Fsingtao%2F20200219a150710.jpg&h=a724b956&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港航空早前陷入財困，加上本港因為新冠肺炎的打擊，港航繼削逾百內地航班後，再向部分員工發出解僱信，通知他們今日（19日）為最後一個上班日，僱用期會在一個月後終止。公司於信中感謝員工的付出，又指會於最後受僱日的7日內，向他們發出3月份的薪金。<br />\n<br />\n港航主席侯偉早前向員工發信，宣布公司計劃裁員約400人，相當於整體員工約一成。又要求在港的地勤人員由前日開始，至6月期間每月放至少2星期無薪假，或每星期工作3日；同時港航空中服務員及機師亦須放無薪假。"},{"pid":"cce717f59bdfb24602514368dedf023d8af0de7f","tid":1887092,"uid":204539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T10:08:51.000Z","msg":"釋放勞動力 好事嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95a27d3b32a3b7a7b903523ece5a391f75d6c73f","tid":1887092,"uid":154763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T10:12:50.000Z","msg":"呢間野本身都唔掂依家只係搵個藉口去炒人，無壞嘅，至少賠足比你，好過佢破產時都唔知要追幾耐。"}]}